tue.yellow

Class ListTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • tue.yellow.ListTracker

  • public class ListTracker
extends java.lang.Object
    The class ListTracker keeps track of all the objects in the emergency department. For each type of object (Nurse, Doctor, Patient, Bed, Chair), lists are kept, which allows for certain methods to for example find the first available doctor.

    One could view two separate ListTracker objects as two different Emergency Rooms.

    Author:
    Team Yellow
